RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.4.2" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

Visit https://phy.wiki for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES in 1.4.2
======================

* Fixed error when searching for enabled bundles
* Check permissions to write files. Allow to search when the user has read permissions.
* Added a new action to copy a bundle
* Launch system databases updates in parallel 
